data.title: primecutsmusic
data.text:
December stock update & news! Clearance sale continues!!

After 15 years & 40 releases, the time has come to wind the clock down on Prime Cuts Music & the next few months will see label closing down gradually. So in saying that, from here on in is a closing down sale until everything is gone!! Thanks to everyone who has supported Prime Cuts Music in anyway, shape or form over the years & if you can support just one last time & buy yourself a bargain at the catalogue listed below. Help me offload what is left!!! Every purchase receives a free Prime Cuts Music cd release & eco friendly carry bag! Cheers & Beers, Dysie.

Email pcuts@ to make an order or enquiries.

Payments can be made with paypal or direct debit.
